				<h3>Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h3>

				<p>Here are answers to some of the more frequently asked questions about CHLA. Questions dealing with searching and navigating this site are addressed on the Help page, and a narrative about the project is on our <a href="/collections/chla/about" aria-label="About CHLA">About</a> page. As always, if you have further questions about this site or its contents please <a href="/collections/chla/contact" aria-label="Contact CHLA">contact us</a> for assistance.</p>
